{"tid":1158324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國一部F-16戰機墜毀加州大樓 飛行員彈射逃生","createTime":"2019-05-17T01:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T01:44:27.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"82fdbd5a59c50f2615d4b3bad0fb16fa23637d56","tid":1158324,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:30:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wwkgZ5bD_Ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwwkgZ5bD_Ts&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=af49175a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wwkgZ5bD_Ts</a><br />\n影片來源：FOX 10 Phoenix YouTube頻道<br />\n<br />\n（中央社洛杉磯16日綜合外電報導）「洛杉磯時報」報導，一架F-16戰機今天撞上南加州馬奇空軍基地（March Air Reserve Base）一棟商業大樓，引發火警。<br />\n<br />\n馬奇空軍基地副消防總長哈勒戴（Timothy Holliday）告訴「洛杉磯時報」（Los Angeles Times），飛行員在戰機於下午3時45分墜毀前彈射逃生。<br />\n<br />\n哈勒戴說，火勢沒有很大。目前還不清楚現場是否有人受傷。（譯者：張曉雯/核稿：盧映孜）1080517<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZxiJ36k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZxiJ36k.png&h=ef9a2955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201905170018.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201905170018.aspx&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=ed09284e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201905170018.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"eb27998ddcb6848cd4295e54b44ad5f7110ee0a9","tid":1158324,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:33:24.000Z","msg":"有懷疑過飛行系統係咪比強國/戰鬥民族入侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個月兩單，F35/F16 波音兩架飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353d1041a43ec3dc1c950f8b70403eb2bb117cf1","tid":1158324,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:41:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5481e74f30f1aa707bc7c8cccb2b84370d4e4595","tid":1158324,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"353d1041a43ec3dc1c950f8b70403eb2bb117cf1","tid":1158324,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:41:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:44:27.000Z","msg":"美國一架F-16戰機於當地時間16日下午返回加州馬奇空軍基地（March Air Reserve Base）之前撞進基地附近一處倉庫墜毀。飛行員彈射逃生後已送醫治療，狀況目前尚不明朗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該係貨倉唔係大樓"}]}